Description: 
        # Large text file reader.
        
        ## usage:
        ```
        from readlargefile.line_reader import LineReader
        
        with LineReader(file_name, max_line, sep) as reader:
            # line is <class 'bytes'>
            for line in reader:
                if line:
                    print(line)
                elif line == b'':
                    print('empty line.')
                else:
                    # line == None
                    print('line is too long.')
        ```
        
